text: Stickney is the largest crater on Phobos. Phobos is a satellite of Mars. It is at and is in diameter. It makes a large part of the moon's surface. It is named after Chloe Angeline Stickney Hall, wife of Phobos's discoverer, Asaph Hall. ==References== ==Other websites== * Flight around Phobos (animated movie) * Stickney in High Resolution Category:Impact craters Category:Moons of Mars
